# Sampler source material for the render-host scenarios. Two kinds live here,
# neither belongs in the repo: the user's own sample library (large, and not
# ours to redistribute), and material bounced from Spotykach itself by
# scenarios like assets_percussive_source.json, which is regenerable. A
# scenario referencing a missing input fails loudly, which is the right
# behaviour -- it is not silently rendered as silence.
# Generator scripts (e.g. gen_clicks.py) are code, not sample material --
# tracked so the material they write is reproducible from a clean checkout.
/host/render/scenarios/assets/*
!/host/render/scenarios/assets/*.py
